Description: REST API and tools for PipeWire audio control
 A REST API server and command-line tools for controlling PipeWire audio parameters.
 .
 Features:
  - REST API for remote PipeWire control
  - Command-line parameter management tool (pw-param)
  - Systemd integration for automatic service startup
  - Real-time audio parameter manipulation
